graphicslib3D

Class Matrix3D.MatrixInvert

  • java.lang.Object
    • graphicslib3D.Matrix3D.MatrixInvert
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Enclosing class:
    Matrix3D

    public class Matrix3D.MatrixInvert
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class is a helper class supporting the Matrix3D class; it is not intended to be used directly. To obtain the inverse of a Matrix3D object, use the method inverse() in the Matrix3D class. the code for this class was based on the source code of Matrix4d.java of the vecmath package in Java3D, written by Kenji Hiranabe of Eiwa System Management,Inc. Aug 2016 - moved into Matrix3D as a sub(helper) class.
